### List available modalities
GET http://localhost:8000/biometric/modalities
Accept: application/json

### Enroll face samples for demo user
POST http://localhost:8000/biometric/face/enroll
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "demo_user",
  "samples": [
    "sample_frame_1",
    "sample_frame_2"
  ]
}

### Verify sample against stored embeddings
POST http://localhost:8000/biometric/face/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sample": "sample_frame_1",
  "top_k": 3
}

### Retrieve stored user information
GET http://localhost:8000/biometric/face/demo_user
Accept: application/json

### Delete demo user
DELETE http://localhost:8000/biometric/face/demo_user1
Accept: application/json

